Founded in 2007, APO Group (formerly known as African Press Organization) is a leading media relations' consulting firm in Africa and the Middle East. The company owns and manages Africa Wire and MENA Wire, press release distribution services focusing on Africa and the Middle East and is the sole press release wire in Africa, as well as Video Newswire, a broadcast-quality video production service distributing videos to up to 1000 news TV channels across Africa, the Middle East, and the world.
Its headquarters is in Lausanne, Switzerland, with offices in Senegal, Dubai and Hong Kong.
